{{!-- Shared "Source" block for bespoke item config views — which book /
      supplement the item is from. Free text (system.source).

      Self-contained (section + grid + row) so it drops into any per-type
      template uniformly, with or without an existing Procurement grid.

      The value root differs per caller (config views render against
      `source.*`), so the caller passes the value in:
        {{> "systems/witcher-ttrpg-death-march/templates/item/partials/source-field.hbs" value=source.source}}
      The submit name is always system.source. --}}
<div class="wdm-cfg-section">{{localize "WITCHER.Item.Source"}}</div>
<div class="wdm-cfg-grid">
  <label class="wdm-cfg-row"><span>{{localize "WITCHER.Item.SourceBook"}}</span>
    <input type="text" name="system.source" value="{{value}}"
           placeholder="{{localize "WITCHER.Item.SourcePlaceholder"}}" />
  </label>
</div>
